golden_transcript:
Agent: Thank you for calling University Health. If you're experiencing a medical emergency, hang up now and dial 911 immediately. How can I assist you today?
User: Can you help me rescheduling the appointment, please?
Agent: Sure, I can help you with rescheduling your appointment. First, I'll need to verify your identity. Can you please tell me your date of birth?
User: January 1st, 1990
Agent: Thank you. Now, could you please say and spell out your last name for me? For example, Smith, S-M-I-T-H.
User: Thank you. Bye bye.
Agent: Just to confirm, did you mean Cadence, spelled C-A-D-E-N-C-E?
User: કાડિંસિસંાસં ક్યે ડિકારિંસીરિં વિ યનસિ વિ
User: Yes.
Agent: Thanks for sharing your last name. Lastly, may I have your ZIP code?
User: 7 8 2 2 8
Agent: Thank you, Billy Cadence. I've found your records and we can proceed with rescheduling your appointment. Let me fetch your upcoming appointments.
Agent: You have an appointment on August 22nd, 2025, at 8:00 AM with Syed Ahsan. Would you like to reschedule this appointment?
Agent: Alright, since you don't want to reschedule this appointment, is there anything else I can assist you with today?
User: No, thanks.
User: No thanks.
Agent: Thank you for calling University Health, Billy. Have a nice day! Goodbye!
